></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=17650743\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=7d7b6425\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"63119acc6f9155e65ebae0acac28b253c6cb8d77","tid":1670344,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7902a0df507d61b4edbe9d4d0430d10612e0ef86","tid":1670344,"uid":26959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae693ba8e5c6b8526c0f4c6e19a35c494b4db6f2","tid":1670344,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"我要見到哩個post上熱門！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"1f3c51e0592c0e3e702cb62a5ff108093a318694","tid"